<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.399582>
    dc:description "FIGURES 89 – 96. Physiphora clausa (90 – 91, holotype ♀ Chrysomyza clausa, MHNP; 92 – 93, syntypes of Musca aenea, ZMUC; 89, 94 – 96, non-type specimens, UAE, SIZK): 89, habitus, left, anterior and dorsal; 90, habitus, left; 91, labels of holotype; 92, habitus and label; 93, 96, wing; 94 – 95, head, left and anterior. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/399582/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.399583>
    dc:description "FIGURES 97 – 105. Physiphora clausa: 97, ♂ phallus; 98, glans, enlarged; 99, epandrium and hypandrium, right; 100, epandrium, anterior; 101, hypandrium, ventral; 102, ♀, aculeus; 103, same, tip, enlarged; 104, vagina and ventral receptacle, ventral; 105, spermathecae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/399583/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

